== 等级和成绩平均绩点（CGPA） ==
STPM采用成绩平均绩点（{{lang|en|Cumulative Grade Point Average}}，CGPA）来计算考生的成绩<ref>{{cite web|title=New assessment system for STPM|url=http://thestar.com.my/education/story.asp?file= /2012/6/3/education/11362890&sec=education|accessdate=3 June 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121020093332/http://thestar.com.my/education|archivedate=2012-10-20}}</ref>。同时，考生的成绩也会根据11个等级来评级，它们分别是A、A-、B+、B、B-、C+、C、C-、D+、D，而F则是不及格的等级。每个等级的平均绩点则从最高的4.0至最低的1.0，考获F等级的考生不获任何绩点，即0.0分<ref>{{cite web|title=New assessment system for STPM|url=http://thestar.com.my/education/story.asp?file=/2012/6/3/education/11362890&sec=education|accessdate=3 June 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121020093332/http://thestar.com.my/education/story.asp?file=%2F2012%2F6%2F3%2Feducation%2F11362890&sec=education|archivedate=2012年10月20日}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=STPM Form 6 Academic Grading System 2012|url=http://berryberryeasy.com/2012/06/stpm-form-6-academic-grading-system-2012/|accessdate=16 June 2012|archive-date=2012-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120620205747/http://berryberryeasy.com/2012/06/stpm-form-6-academic-grading-system-2012/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

